# Teno Neu V2 — proxy.txt
#
# Add one proxy per line (lines starting with # are ignored).
# Supported formats:
#   ip:port
#   http://ip:port
#   http://username:password@ip:port
#   username:password@ip:port
#
# Proxies are assigned round-robin across accounts.
# This file is optional – leave it empty (or delete it) to run without proxies.
